{"tid":1855391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳在過去一日暴增60宗確診病例 林奠：全面封關不切實際","createTime":"2020-02-01T05:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T14:25:53.000Z","uid":212626,"like":158,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"d55f2cf1c4b176a43003dc3757aa2dd08aa2694b","tid":1855391,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:14:27.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情不斷擴大，其中廣東昨日新增127個確診個案，令到確診個案增至520宗。深圳在過去一日新增60宗確診病例，令到累積個案增至170宗，成為省內最多人感染的城市。當局分析，其中的117宗屬於輸入個案，16宗是在深圳感染，1宗仍在調查。以地區計，南山、福田區多，分別有35宗及31宗。<br />\n<br />\n當局昨公佈確診病人曾經出現過的82個地點，同樣以南山、福田區最多，大部份都是屋苑，不過，名單中還包括南山區中洲萬豪酒店、大鵬新區萬豪酒店。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200201/OFDMV2C3DZ7XW3VA2Q6P4GSHBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200201%2FOFDMV2C3DZ7XW3VA2Q6P4GSHBA%2F&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5In6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=46b3c9be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200201%2FOFDMV2C3DZ7XW3VA2Q6P4GSHBA%2F&h=5b6b789a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200201/OFDMV2C3DZ7XW3VA2Q6P4GSHBA/</a>"},{"pid":"55557a2fbd7c6d2504ff4b4da53b32f90172dd2d","tid":1855391,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2123fa4f5c75429e0549f5b30d962c29337fdf4","tid":1855391,"uid":9640,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HD3SzD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HD3SzD.jpg&h=e01c6f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【全城集氣撐醫護】<br />\n聽日「醫管局員工陣線」會召開特別會